            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Kew July 24/62 ¶ My dear Sir, ¶  ¶ My letter dated the 14th I believe was finished on the post day (last Saturday) and despatched to save the post via Southampton — That same evening arrived yours of ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">62.07.24</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From George Bentham</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M4, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>Published in part in Moyal (1976) pp. 180-1.</p>
               </note>Kew July 24/62<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>MS annotation at head of letter by M: 'Portrait'.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>My letter dated the 14th I believe was finished on the post day (last Saturday) and despatched to save the post via Southampton — That same evening arrived yours of the 23rd May to which I now reply briefly via Marseilles</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>My former letters will have informed you of the safe arrival of the first second and third cases of your plants and of the redespatch to you of the first (including <name key="Pittosporeae">Pittosporeae</name> or the greater part of the second) per Norfolk</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The 4th case per Orwell is not yet arrived. I trust the remainder will follow soon My previous letters will have given you the order I follow as far as I have gone After <name key="Caryophylleae">Caryophylleae</name> come (including only those Orders which are found in Australia where I believe are no <name key="Guttiferae">Guttiferae</name>
               <name key="Ternstroemiaceae">Ternstroemiaceae</name> etc):</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <table n="Table1">
               <row>
                  <cell style="padding-left: 0.0556in; padding-right: 0.0556in; padding-top: 0in; padding-bottom: 0in; border: none; ">
